---
import BlogPost from '../../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import { posts } from '../../data/blog-posts';

const post = posts.find(p => p.slug === 'healthcare-communication-analytics')!;
---

<BlogPost title={post.title} date={post.date}>
  <div class="mb-8 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
    {post.tags.map(tag => (
      <a href={`/blog?tag=${tag}`} class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200">
        #{tag}
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>

  <p>Implementing speech analytics in healthcare requires careful planning and adherence to best practices to ensure maximum benefit and regulatory compliance.</p>

  <h2>Key Implementation Strategies</h2>
  <p>Successful implementation of healthcare communication analytics involves:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Clear objectives and metrics</li>
    <li>Staff training and buy-in</li>
    <li>Privacy and compliance measures</li>
    <li>Regular assessment and adjustment</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Measuring Success</h2>
  <p>Track these key performance indicators to evaluate your analytics program:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Patient satisfaction scores</li>
    <li>Communication efficiency metrics</li>
    <li>Clinical outcome improvements</li>
    <li>Staff engagement levels</li>
  </ul>
</BlogPost>